            "mimetype": "text/plain",
            "body": "Customer: Hi, I'm calling about my recent bill. I think there's an error.\nAgent: Hello! I'd be happy to help you with your billing question. Can you provide your account number?\nCustomer: Sure, it's 123456789.\nAgent: Thank you. I can see your account. What specific issue are you seeing with the bill?\nCustomer: I was charged $50 for a service I never used."
